textcontent: Multiple choice is quick and addictive.
It makes the learning easy.
It gives the learner a sense of success.
However, it will be nice to have another set of tests where the vocabulary is shown in a sentence and the learner needs to write the meaning.
I don't know whether the technology can handle the various options that come in and evaluate the acceptable ones to give a positive reward.
Nevertheless, the learner will eventually learn the acceptable answers and type in the proper words.
it's a great app for building vocabulary.
although it needs to have something like translation to other languages, but it works really good, helping you to learn the words with examples and repeating them!
this app is also very easy to use!
Great vocabulary builder.
The GUI is simple and attractive.
I've been using it for the GRE in addition to my anki deck.
I recommend using this app and creating an anki deck for the words you don't know.
Anki will tax your active recall more, since you don't have options to choose from, but this app will nevertheless give you an initiation into those words and how they're used.
Great free resource!
Its an excellent application.

I liked it alot just I have posted 4 stars in the rating because I have a suggestion that when the answer is given by the learner there come's a example I think with that you should give a simplified definition which will be in sentence which we can easily see on Google so that we can understand the word easily and can quickly memorize it .
But living this aside the application is superb.‚ò∫
Great interface.
The examples are not always viewd completely.
Sometimes I have to google the meaning of the meaning of the word that's provided.
More synonyms and meanings could help.
Incorrect word definitions.
Started using this app to build my vocabulary and I noticed that some of the words such as "gleaned" and "facetious" had definitions that really do not corroborate with notable dictionaries.
Often these more complex words do not have direct synonyms and this apps' attempt to define words through synonyms alone is misleading.
Brilliantly organized and easy to use.
App words teaching engine is so good that it's impossible to forget the words you learn from it.
Great work guys!
This app is cool and splendid.
It transform me to a cheerful dispostion.
It solve a persons queries and doubts regarding new advanced words and it act like a motivational speaker,which I can hear a motto "DO IT, DO IT, until YOU SCHOLARY LEARNED".
I recommend this app,where you can sure learn newly words in english without a class.
Everything optimistic!üòäüòçüôãüí™üíñ
I had a good vocabulary already but this app has definitely increased it!
On average about 15% of the words are ones I did not know at all or had heard but never knew the meaning.
Even for the ones I do know already, a refresher is always nice!
Absolutely recommend if you want to increase your vocabulary!
I find it helpful mostly these times that I almost forgot the term of some words, It's fun to play with and at the same I am learning new words.
Thanks!
